# YooBook Project

Simple web app untuk buku dengan login, register, contact form, dan filter buku.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JS, Bootstrap
- Backend: Node.js, Express, bcrypt
- Database: PostgreSQL (pg)

## Features
- Register & Login user (password hashed)
- Submit contact form
- Search & filter buku
- Navbar update berdasarkan status login

## Database
### Users
id, name, email, password, created_at

### Contacts
id, user_id (nullable), first_name, last_name, email, phone, subject, message, created_at

## CRUD
- Create: register, contact
- Read: login, filter buku
- Update & Delete: belum ada

## Run
1. Install: `npm install express cors pg bcrypt`
2. Buat DB & tabel PostgreSQL
3. Jalankan: `node server.js`
4. Buka HTML di browser
